---
import Base from "../layouts/base.astro";
---

<Base title="Clarity. — What is Insight-as-a-Service?">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-24 text-center">
    <!-- Heading sits visually above the box -->
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">
        What is Insight-as-a-Service?
      </h1>

    <!-- Insight-as-a-Service Explainer -->
    <section
      class="mt-[1rem] bg-gray-900 text-white py-16 px-6 rounded-lg text-center"
    >
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Big decisions. Limited time. Incomplete data. <br />
        Sound familiar? You're not alone.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-4 opacity-90">
        Traditional consultancies feel bloated. Hiring full-time is slow.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 opacity-90">
        That's why we created Insight-as-a-Service — a flexible, strategic
        support plan that delivers expert insight on tap, not just once, but
        continuously.
      </p>

      <p class="text-xl font-semibold">
        It's not advice. It's forward motion, delivered.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Insight Grid -->
    <section class="mt-20 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-left">
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-center mb-2">How It Works</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-center">
          Pick a plan. We plug in. <br />
          Regular sessions → focused insights → actionable Clarity.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-center mb-2">Why It Works</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-center">
          Clarity. compounds. <br />
          We embed over time. You make better decisions — faster and more confidently,
          with less risk.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-center mb-2">What's Included</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-left">
          → Expert facilitation<br />
          → Decision-making support<br />
          → Clear: priorities, blockers, recommendations<br />
          → Ongoing access. Not one-and-done.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-center mb-2">Who It's For</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-center">
          Product leaders. Enterprise decision-makers. <br />
          Anyone who needs to align fast, reduce noise, and unlock value.<br /> Without
          extra headcount or bureaucracy.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section
      id="final-cta"
      class="mt-20 bg-gray-900 text-white py-12 px-6 rounded-lg text-center"
    >
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Still unsure?</h2>
      <p class="mb-6 text-lg">
        That's why Clarity exists.<br /> You don't need all the answers, just a better
        way to find them. <br /><br />No fluff. No spam. Just Clarity.<br /><br
        />
      </p>
      <a
        href="/"
        class="inline-block bg-white text-black font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-gray-200 transition"
        >Join the Waitlist</a
      >
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
